[[File:Pz4kv7T.png|thumb|295x295px]] {{Infobox |Box title = Blade93 |Row 1 title = Occupation: |Row 1 info = mercenary |Row 2 title = Weapons: |Row 2 info = Diamond Sword, Diamond Bow |Row 3 title = Affliction:|Row 3 info = Himself, Mylas, The TNT Griefer Organization|Row 4 title = Residence: |Row 4 info = None |Row 5 title = Age: |Row 5 info = unknown}}
Blade93 is a mercenary who works for [[Mynlas]], a griefer and the head of the griefer organization known as The TNT Griefer Organization.
== Description == Blade93 operates like a ghost. This means no one knows who he is, his age or when he was born. Blade93 will accept any contract if the payment is right. Blade93 is a skilled swordsman, being able to take on over 100 players with ease. Blade93 is equally skilled in archery to the point where he can shoot arrows from miles away. He is wanted in 100 servers for killing at least 100 000 players. [[Category:Players]]

