== Backstory == [[Category:Players]]

[[File:Herobrine's_Palace.jpg|thumb|Herobrine's Palace. A.K.A. The Great Devastation.]] "Prepare to see the end of your Minecraftia...And the beginning of mine..." -Herobrine to Notch
The Great Devastation is Herobrine's palace and base of operations. At the end of ''The Chronicles of Minecraftia'', Herobrine gathers everyone the heroes met during their adventure here for his final twisted plot to conquer Minecraftia. A great battle between Notch's armies and Herobrine's armies happens here.[[File:Minecraft_herobrine_head_by_xminyoungie-d50a6qt.png|thumb|The Master's Head. The 3rd Boss Battle found in the Great Devastation.]]
